author: Corridor Crew
description:
Throwback to when Seth Rogen joined the Corridor couch to break down one of the many VFX scenes from This Is the End, the 2013 hit movie that he starred in, co-produced, co-wrote, and co-directed with Evan Goldberg.
Paul Linden was the VFX supervisor from the studio Modus FX, which delivered over 240 VFX shots for the movie.

Do you think the CG monster still holds up to today?
title: Why Seth Rogen's Monster was CGI
